21d4			 
21d4			 
21d4			; 
21d4			; 
21d4			; define linked list: 
21d4			; 
21d4			; 1. compiled byte op code 
21d4			; 2. len of text word 
21d4			; 3. text word 
21d4			; 4. ptr to next dictionary word 
21d4			; 5. asm, calls etc for the word 
21d4			; 
21d4			;  if 1 == 0 then last word in dict  
21d4			;   
21d4			; set the start of dictionary scanning to be in ram and the last word point to the system dict 
21d4			;  
21d4			;  
21d4			; create basic standard set of words 
21d4			; 
21d4			;  
21d4			; + - / * DUP EMIT . SWAP IF..THEN..ELSE DO..LOOP  : ; DROP  
21d4			; 2DUP 2DROP 2SWAP  
21d4			; @ C@ - get byte  
21d4			; ! C! - store byte 
21d4			; 0< true if less than zero 
21d4			; 0= true if zero 
21d4			; < >  
21d4			; = true if same 
21d4			; variables 
21d4			 
